WEBVTT

00:01.200 --> 00:05.020
I’ll still keep fighting for you, Lain. So don't worry.

00:06.190 --> 00:09.610
There must be some reason why you’ve been hallucinating.

00:11.740 --> 00:12.870
I wonder what it might be.

00:13.680 --> 00:16.510
Things seem to be going all right for her at home.

00:16.700 --> 00:19.530
There aren’t any congenital injuries.

00:20.790 --> 00:23.070
She sees images of specific things.

00:23.310 --> 00:25.260
There must be a reason.

00:27.620 --> 00:29.790
But what am I writing this down for?

00:32.110 --> 00:33.100
I’m going to bed.
